      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Step into automotive perfection with this absolute gem! This vehicle is in pristine, mint condition and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Every detail has been meticulously maintained, from the flawless exterior to the spotless interior. It's truly a rare find for a discerning buyer who wants the very best quality and a like-new driving experience!",
