    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, representing the absolute best example you will find on the market. It has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showing zero signs of wear on the exterior paint or the premium interior upholstery. Mechanically, it performs exactly as it did the day it left the showroom, with every component functioning flawlessly and a complete service history to back it up. For a collector or a discerning buyer who demands perfection, this car offers a rare opportunity to own a virtually new vehicle.",
