    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, minor door dings, and some fading on the clear coat in certain spots. Inside, the cabin is functional but shows wear on the upholstery and some minor staining on the carpets. Mechanically, the car starts up consistently and the engine runs fine, though it may require more frequent maintenance than a newer model. It is a solid choice for someone looking for affordable, basic transportation.",
