      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition. The exterior has visible scratches and several small dents. The interior shows signs of regular use, including wear on the upholstery and minor staining on the carpets. All mechanical components are functional, though the car exhibits the expected wear for its age.",
      "price": 20000.0,
